{"tid":1841661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[致所有HA同事] 唔好以為去隔離病房好大愛 你只係服務緊班大陸人","createTime":"2020-01-25T10:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:06:54.000Z","uid":252124,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3018232830e0355b386dc1fea53e45c062116020","tid":1841661,"uid":252124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"首先多謝傳媒記者朋友幫手喺記者會度問嘅問題<br />\n特別多謝now記者 真係問咗我想知嘅嘢<br />\n林鄭話相信只有部分醫護會罷工<br />\n仲話罷工係激進行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹係內科病房嘅註冊護士<br />\n抽籤係頭幾批將要去隔離病房嘅人<br />\n聽完成個記招 來來去去都係講抗疫<br />\n防疫就淨係取消武漢高鐵同飛機 同叫人自行通報<br />\n<br />\n我希望各位同事知清楚<br />\n隔離病房收嘅懷疑個案 其實得小部分真係香港人<br />\n好多都係大陸人黎 有啲連香港身分證都冇<br />\n就算本身唔係住武漢 都曾經去過武漢 或者住過大陸醫院<br />\n然後黎香港嘅理由話係探親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係點解堅持要封關嘅原因<br />\n除咗驚感染咗嘅人走落黎會傳染之外<br />\n班大陸人根本就走晒黎香港做body check<br />\n佔用咗寶貴嘅負壓隔離病房<br />\n犧牲緊原本應該俾番香港人嘅資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSARS嗰陣我仲讀緊中學<br />\n讀U揀得nursing 攞得個牌<br />\n就預咗類似SARS嘅疫症終有一日會再發生<br />\n幫番不幸受感染嘅香港人 有乜問題？ 根本預咗<br />\n但係因為防疫冇把關令到班大陸人衝晒落嚟<br />\n不了 我真係做唔到咁大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺工會罷工細節未正式公佈前<br />\n小妹會先sick leave<br />\n冇計啦 原本我就係激進嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2b4a93a1188352d103cad038f006766c92dd23","tid":1841661,"uid":79680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5JiAy9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5JiAy9.png&h=fe60e6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[推上去] 罷工比返工救得更多嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"428d4ec64f1f17c659e5527d1a7a716fc242465d","tid":1841661,"uid":53758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"Resign 保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想因為支那人冇咗條命"},{"pid":"1f0d18ba5c12b533d769940aae2196af9b864d26","tid":1841661,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"abaed664202eafe267d34fb52ccd714ae6714231","tid":1841661,"uid":153808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"支持黃嘅罷工 等班藍到仆街嘅醫生上戰場"},{"pid":"60da16908875423833159868786aa62f1c0beb05","tid":1841661,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3c3aa0141f97610b6f00f2e194397157df6741","tid":1841661,"uid":280886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb2b4a93a1188352d103cad038f006766c92dd23","tid":1841661,"uid":79680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5JiAy9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5JiAy9.png&h=fe60e6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[推上去] 罷工比返工救得更多嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"正啊張圖!<br />\n<br />\n如果認同請幫推幫share <img src=\"/assets/fa